## Final Verdict

**The site is launch-ready at the MVP level**, but the three P0 items (especially the `next/dynamic` anti-pattern silently breaking your Ventures data fetching) should be resolved immediately. The security posture is solid for a solo-founder operation, and the design system is remarkably consistent. Address the P0 and P1 items before promoting to production, and schedule the P2/P3 items for your first post-launch sprint.
